title: How do I transfer data from Samsung Calender to Google Calender on Pixel 4a?
content: I have been using the Samsung Calender on my old Galaxy S7 for years and want to transfer the data to my new Pixel 4a. Did the 'set up' transfer of all other data (which worked) however the calender data didn't transfer. Any ideas?
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 4a
